</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>先是<pc>，</pc>吐蕃與回鶻爭北庭<pc>，</pc>大戰<pc>，</pc>死傷頗眾<pc>，</pc>徵兵<measure quantity="10000" unit="people">
<num value="10000">萬</num>人</measure>於雲南<pc>。</pc>異牟尋辭以國小<pc>，</pc>請發<measure quantity="3000" unit="people">
<num value="3000">三千</num>人</measure>
<pc>，</pc>吐蕃少之<pc>。</pc>益至<num value="5000">五千</num>
<pc>，</pc>乃許之<pc>。</pc>異牟尋遣<measure quantity="5000" unit="people">
<num value="5000">五千</num>人</measure>前行<pc>，</pc>自將數<measure quantity="10000" unit="people">
