<num value="4">四</num>月</measure>
<pc>，</pc>
<num value="7">庚午</num>
<pc>，</pc>宣武軍亂<pc>，</pc>留後李<num value="10000">萬</num>榮討平之<pc>。</pc>先是<pc>，</pc>宣武親兵<measure quantity="300" unit="people">
