</div>
<div>
<p>其<num value="1">一</num>
<pc>，</pc>論兩稅之弊<pc>，</pc>其略曰<pc>：</pc>
<pc>「</pc>
<quote>舊制賦役之法<pc>，</pc>曰租<pc>、</pc>調<pc>、</pc>庸<pc>。</pc>丁男<measure quantity="1" unit="people">
